Articles.Content: I'm back from a two-month UN volunteering service in Afghanistan. So what happened while I was gone?
Well, not much actually. (Not sure if you know about .23.5 the ARM update) But Welcome Back!

Hey, welcome back! And thanks for your service.

V0.23.5 is out now. It came out at the beginning of Apr, so I'm not sure if you saw it. There are now extra large (size 3) parts, and capturable asteroids!

Good luck and have fun!

-Claw
